text: Gerald Dupuis (10 August 1904 - 8 August 1960) was a Canadian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1928 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1904 births Category:1960 deaths Category:Canadian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Canada Category:Ski jumpers at the 1928 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Montreal
